imdb.plot outline: 'Whiz Kids' is a comedy webseries about two very different twentysomething girls who become unlikely allies while trying to figure out how to get out of their sandwich-making day jobs. From their daily hijinks at the shop, dealing with guy problems, and trying to not get fired on a daily basis, 'Whiz Kids' is about what happens when your plan B becomes your reality.
